"""
    isTwofoldIntervalPCMContainingIntervalPCM(
        A,
        𝒜;
        strict=false
    )

Check if the interval PCM `A` is contained in the twofold interval PCM `𝒜`.
Throws a `DimensionMismatch` if the sizes of the given matrices `A` and `𝒜` are not the same.
